42:33.053 --> 42:34.855
slots that come open. So, you come up again for 
promotion. You only come up about four times. And

42:43.749 --> 42:45.051
you come up every year? Yeah, you come up every year 
for four years for the general officer. And then

42:51.894 --> 42:58.948
last time you come up and you're number two on the 
list. You get promoted almost immediately when

42:58.968 --> 43:02.074
the list comes up. And so that's what happened. 
That could be some praise.

43:16.300 --> 43:19.725
Oh, God, you know, I don't complain about that. I 
know about all that sort

43:19.745 --> 43:24.433
of stuff. In other words, Mr. McNamara was really 
happy with the quality of work that you were doing.

43:29.821 --> 43:31.824
Yeah, he was very happy. In fact, I had my first 
Distinguished Service Medal, my first medal that

43:31.884 --> 43:43.843
they normally reserve for general officers, 
which is the highest award you can get in service,

43:31.884 --> 43:43.843
Distinguished Service Medal. was when I was a 
colonel.

