Why do you think that you were, when you first came 
up, the first time you came up for general, why do

43:53.545 --> 44:03.018
you think that you were number 66? Especially 
considering your career. Yeah, I think because

44:07.364 --> 44:13.172
whoever was on that board, whoever the six 
generals were on that board liked 65 guys better

44:15.430 --> 44:18.296
than they did me. Maybe one of those guys on the 
board, I don't know, was the one that I forced a

44:19.418 --> 44:28.638
memorandum down his throat to get something done 
